{"type":"message","id":"5482e014","parentId":"712c10ef","timestamp":"2026-03-25T06:02:33.197Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is complaining that the system sent her buy candidates that aren't actually recommended for buying, especially for someone with no position. She's questioning why the system is sending her stocks to \"buy\" when the AI decision is actually \"reduce/hold\" and not suitable for empty-handed investors.\n\nThis is a valid critique. The system generated a \"买入候选 TOP3\" but the AI decisions on those stocks are actually BLOCK or reduce/观望 - not actual buy signals. This seems like a disconnect between the scoring/ranking system and the actual AI decision engine.\n\nI need to acknowledge this feedback and possibly note this as an issue to be addressed - the candidate pool report ranks by score but doesn't filter out stocks that AI has actually BLOCKED or marked as unsuitable for new positions. This is a product logic issue worth addressing.\n\nLet me respond acknowledging the valid point.","thinkingSignature":"672266f00667e6c43c668670b422d8051c51eeae2e9bb93f0d568432190f03bb"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 说得很对，这是系统的逻辑问题。\n\n候选池是按**评分排序**筛选出来的，评分高就进候选名单、就推送，但**没有联动 AI 决策状态**做二次过滤。导致：\n\n- 天华新能评分 0.883 → 进候选 → TOP2 → 但 AI 已 BLOCK\n- 腾景科技评分 0.887 → 进候选 → TOP1 → 但 AI 建议观望（对空仓者不适用）\n\n系统把\"评分高\"等同于\"推荐买\"，忽略了 AI 风控的结论，这是一个需要修复的点。\n\n可以改成：**只有 AI 决策为\"买入\"或\"持有\"（且非 BLOCK）才进入候选推荐**，评分只做同梯队内的排序依据。\n\n要不要我提一个优化：候选推荐前增加 AI 决策状态门禁，从根本上避免这类误推送？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120,"output":354,"cacheRead":53866,"cacheWrite":1321,"totalTokens":55661,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774418536195}}
