{"type":"message","id":"354a3cd8","parentId":"94864514","timestamp":"2026-03-25T06:05:26.173Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `generate_candidate_pool_report.py` is the one that generates the candidate pool report. Let me look at it.","thinkingSignature":"97ab01e8c7ba91811d76692cdc73d2424013df83f58d7eba91056dac2aa65c12"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s36evwy5smx9_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_candidate_pool_report.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":18034,"output":78,"cacheRead":38743,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56855,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774418722686}}
{"type":"message","id":"598d0740","parentId":"354a3cd8","timestamp":"2026-03-25T06:05:26.246Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_s36evwy5smx9_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\nfrom __future__ import annotations\n\nimport argparse\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nimport pandas as pd\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    ap = argparse.ArgumentParser()\n    ap.add_argument(\"--trade-date\", required=True)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--merged-signal\", required=True)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--merged-approved\", required=True)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--merged-orders\", required=True)\n    ap.add_argument(\"--output\", default=None)\n    args = ap.parse_args()\n\n    merged_signal = pd.read_csv(args.merged_signal)\n    merged_approved = pd.read_csv(args.merged_approved)\n    merged_orders = pd.read_csv(args.merged_orders)\n\n    trade_tag = args.trade_date.replace('-', '')\n    if args.output:\n        out = Path(args.output)\n    else:\n        base = Path(__file__).resolve().parents[1]\n        out = base / 'research' / 'reports' / f'candidate_pool_report_{trade_tag}.md'\n\n    buy_count = int((merged_orders['action'] == 'BUY').sum()) if 'action' in merged_orders.columns else 0\n    risk_summary = ', '.join(sorted(set(str(x) for x in merged_approved.get('risk_status', pd.Series(dtype=str)).dropna())))\n    top = merged_orders.sort_values('score', ascending=False).head(5) if 'score' in merged_orders.columns else merged_orders.head(5)\n\n    lines = []\n    lines.append(f'# 候选实盘池日报 {args.trade_date}')\n    lines.append('')\n    lines.append('## 一、候选策略状态')\n    lines.append('| 策略ID | 状态 | 说明 |')\n    lines.append('|---|---|---|')\n    lines.append('| smallcap_chip_v4_1_alpha_guard | Candidate | 稳健对照组 |')\n    lines.append('| smallcap_chip_v4_2_alpha_recover | Candidate | 参与率修复主候选 |')\n    lines.append('| smallcap_chip_v4_2b_fundamental_guard | Candidate | 基本面增强实验组 |')\n    lines.append('')\n    lines.append('## 二、merged signal 摘要')\n    lines.append(f'- merged signal 文件：`{args.merged_signal}`')\n    lines.append(f'- merged approved signal 文件：`{args.merged_approved}`')\n    lines.append(f'- merged proposed orders 文件：`{args.merged_orders}`')\n    lines.append(f'- 标的数：{len(merged_signal)}')\n    lines.append(f'- BUY 数量：{buy_count}')\n    lines.append(f'- 风险状态摘要：{risk_summary or \"normal\"}')\n    lines.append('')\n    lines.append('## 三、今日优先候选（Top 5）')\n    lines.append('| ts_code | action | score | strategy_id |')\n    lines.append('|---|---:|---:|---|')\n    for _, row in top.iterrows():\n        lines.append(f\"| {row.get('ts_code','')} | {row.get('action','')} | {row.get('score','')} | {row.get('strategy_id','')} |\")\n    lines.append('')\n    lines.append('## 四、候选池结论')\n    lines.append('- 当前系统已具备双策略 merged signal 与 merged orders 能力。')\n    lines.append('- 当前状态建议继续作为 Candidate 池观察，不直接视为正式实盘池。')\n    lines.append('- 下一步重点：风险参数外置、状态治理、灰度运行跟踪。')\n    lines.append('')\n    lines.append(f'_Generated at: {datetime.now().astimezone().isoformat()}_')\n\n    out.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    out.write_text('\\n'.join(lines), encoding='utf-8')\n    print(out)\n\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    main()\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774418726223}}
{"type":"message","id":"8508ad52","parentId":"598d0740","timestamp":"2026-03-25T06:05:38.723Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The candidate pool report script itself just reads already-processed merged orders and signals. The issue is upstream - in the pipeline that generates merged proposed orders. The key fix would be to filter out stocks where `ai_decision` is `block` or `reduce` from the candidate pool recommendation.\n\nLet me look at where the merged proposed orders are generated, and where the AI decision filtering should happen. Actually, the most direct fix is to filter the merged orders based on `ai_decision` before generating the candidate report.\n\nBut actually, the real issue is the **candidate pool report** that shows TOP candidates without considering AI decision. The report is `candidate_pool_report_20260310.md`. The report at line 44-46 shows the TOP 5 by score regardless of AI decision.\n \nNow I need to trace where the signal_tickets CSV gets generated - that's the file with the `ai_decision` field that should gate whether something appears in the TOP list. Let me check the prepare_live_signal_tickets.py script to see how signals flow through and where I can apply the filter.","thinkingSignature":"ccd897a5d611b9bb1bc6034b78c8314eb1829d22577a014a8a01e7d1d699ae90"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6z3kgrkh1hc1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"head -5 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_aggressive_signal_tickets_20260325.csv && echo \"---\" && head -5 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_aggressive_merged_approved_signals_20260325.csv"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":18932,"output":332,"cacheRead":38743,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58007,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"tota