{"type":"message","id":"5b6ab0b4","parentId":"568af817","timestamp":"2026-03-25T06:08:51.886Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zhang Ling is asking whether she should also buy 航天电器 (002025.SZ) without a position. Let me check the AI analysis for this stock.\n\nFrom the merged orders data I already have:\n- 002025.SZ 航天电器: ai_decision=pass, ai_advice=买入, ai_trend_prediction=看多, ai_sentiment_score=67, ai_budget_scale=1.0, ai_score_scale=1.0\n\nBut let me check the detailed advice - it says for no-position investors: \"空仓者建议：等待缩量回踩MA5（约64.12元）附近轻仓试错，或回踩MA10（约60.91元）加仓\" - it was trading at 65.43 with -2.4% change at 12:31.\n\n\nThe key difference with 航天电器 is that it has a \"pass\" decision rather than \"reduce\", meaning the AI is giving a genuine buy signal rather than just a hold recommendation. For someone without a position, the strategy would be to wait for a pullback to the MA5 level around 64 yuan before entering.","thinkingSignature":"f01ffa3309a7efa06f8f7c12f556c8557068f5a357c1054e1204ea393847be50"},{"type":"text","text":"好问题。让我查一下航天电器的详细 AI 分析。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n8gff1kywhlw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system && python3 -c \"\nimport pandas as pd\ndf = pd.read_csv('research/reports/paper_aggressive_merged_proposed_orders_20260325.csv')\nrow = df[df['ts_code']=='002025.SZ'].iloc[0]\nprint('AI决策:', row['ai_decision'])\nprint('AI建议:', row['ai_operation_advice'])\nprint('趋势:', row['ai_trend_prediction'])\nprint('情绪评分:', row['ai_sentiment_score'])\nprint('预算系数:', row['ai_budget_scale'])\nprint('空仓建议:', row['ai_no_position_advice'])\nprint('持仓建议:', row['ai_has_position_advice'])\nprint('止损位:', row['ai_stop_loss'])\nprint('实时价:', row['ai_realtime_price'])\nprint('涨跌幅:', row['ai_realtime_change_pct'])\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120,"output"