{"type":"message","id":"f0175aeb","parentId":"27886c7c","timestamp":"2026-03-25T06:09:06.162Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So 002025.SZ 航天电器 has ai_decision=pass and ai_advice=买入, which is the only one that cleared the gate with a genuine \"buy\" signal. However, the AI also says for no-position investors to wait for a pullback to MA5 (~64.12元). The current price is 65.43, which is already above MA5. So the advice is to wait.\n\nHowever, it's worth noting that the price was 65.43 at 12:31, and the current time is 14:08. The price may have changed. Also, the change was -2.4% at 12:31, which means it had already pulled back somewhat.\n\n\nThe core issue is that while 航天电器 is the only TOP5 candidate with a genuine \"buy\" signal, the AI still recommends waiting for a pullback to MA5 for no-position investors—and we're already above that level. I should give Zhang Ling a straightforward answer about whether this stock is appropriate for her situation right now.","thinkingSignature":"dc69c2580a8c724cbde434102ad8a8324410c013879f8a5db5f695eee2021287"},{"type":"text","text":"航天电器是 6 只通过门禁里唯一 AI 决策为 **pass + 买入** 的，但 AI 对空仓者的建议也是\"等回踩\"：\n\n> **空仓者建议**：等待缩量回踩 MA5（约 **64.12 元**）附近轻仓试错，或回踩 MA10（约 60.91 元）加仓。\n\n今日 12:31 实时价 **65.43 元**（-2.4%），当时已高于 MA5，追高也不算安全买价。如果现在价格已经更低接近 MA5，可以考虑；否则同样建议等。\n\n**结论**：航天电器是当前最够格的候选（唯一 pass），但买点上仍需等回踩到 64 元附近，不适合当前位置直接追。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":27713,"output":377,"cacheRead":38743,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66833,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774418932463}}
