{"type":"message","id":"b0fae68d","parentId":"cc930474","timestamp":"2026-03-25T06:09:21.001Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zhang Ling is saying the current price of 航天电器 is 65.57 yuan. The AI's no-position advice was to wait for a pullback to MA5 (~64.12) or MA10 (~60.91). The current price of 65.57 is above MA5, which means it's not at an ideal entry point.\n\nI should be honest - the AI's own advice for people without positions is to wait for the pullback to 64.12 or lower. At 65.57, that's not the safe entry point. I should not encourage buying at the current price just because it passed the AI gate.\n\nI should be clear: the AI decision was \"pass/buy\" meaning it passed the AI risk gate, but the specific entry advice from AI for no-position investors is still \"wait for pullback to MA5 (~64.12)\". At 65.57, it's still elevated and not the recommended entry.","thinkingSignature":"2d612f79418caa32ea629cc53b2509b83b4302d42d5ac95a0f8544612a798df0"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 诚实说：**AI 自己的建议不是现在买。**\n\n航天电器虽然通过了 AI 门禁（pass / 买入 / 评分 0.831），但 AI 对空仓者的建议是：\n\n> \"等待缩量回踩 MA5（约 **64.12 元**）附近轻仓试错\"\n\n现价 65.57 元高于 MA5 约 1.4 元，还不属于安全买价。\n\n可以买的情况：等价格回落到 64~65 区间（接近 MA5），再考虑介入；或者等跌到 MA10（约 60.91 元）加仓位更理想。\n\n当前位置追高，AI 本身也不支持。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120,"output":342,"cacheRead":65305,"cacheWrite":1322,"totalTokens":67089,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774418947594}}
